      "description": "$5,900 - Honest project or budget-priced driver for someone who sees the potential. This poor-condition example shows significant wear and will need attention, but it still has some appeal as an inexpensive entry point for a hands-on buyer or restoration-minded owner. If you want something affordable and you\u2019re not afraid of some work, this could be a worthwhile candidate.",
