    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers straightforward value for buyers seeking dependable basic transportation or a practical project opportunity. It shows age and wear consistent with use, but remains an appealing option for someone who wants an inexpensive way to get on the road without overextending their budget. A sensible choice for commuters, first-time buyers, or anyone looking for affordable utility.",
